Day 11 of Tokyo 2020 did not hold back being an incredibly emotional one! What an unforgettable day! 🤩

Podiums swept, legends created and world records broken! 🔥

A Historic first Para Badminton Gold for Malaysia, back-to-back Sitting Volleyball titles for Iran and soccer ball Brazil win the battle of the South American Football 5-A-Side giants! 

Watch Day 11 Overall Highlights | Tokyo 2020
